title: Billy Zane
itunes:title: Billy Zane
description:
Billy Zane [Titanic, Dead Calm, The Phantom, MacGruber] talks with Anna about MacGruber and how fun it is to say the name of his character (Brigadier Commander Enos Queeth), boat movies, horror conventions, romance, heartbreak, Bond girls, entrepreneurship, dressing for success, and more.


This episode’s Unqualified segment begins with a call from Adam who is looking for some inspiration and practical advice as he goes about changing aspects of his life. Next, Anna and Billy talk with Ariana, who after being cheated on in a previous relationship, is beginning to see red flags in the man she’s currently dating.


Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
